These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: baking, camping
Job: firefighter, paramedic
1. Job:firefighter is in an even position##4
2. Job:paramedic == Hobby:camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | camping | baking |
| Job     | paramedic    | firefighter   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, milk
Sport: snowboarding, soccer
1. Sport:snowboarding is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:milk is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | milk | mirinda        |
| Sport      | snowboarding  | soccer |

 #################################
 
